            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Teachers are friendly but the service are very bad. No importantance of timing, no proper schedule, bad conversation with parents. My daughter is waiting for school bus for one hour continuously from three days. Bus driver dont know the exact rout from where the childrens pic and drop. There is not any person who concern about your problems. Don't recieve phone call if you have any complain. If I know all these things before going to take admission of my child I'll never go for it.",
          "publisher": {
